# Disney Character Warehouse

The Disney Character Warehouse is the name of 3 outlet stores in Florida, one in the Orlando International Premium Outlets, one in the Orlando Vineland Premium Outlets, and one in Sawgrass Mills in Sunrise, FL, that sell discounted surplus merchandise from nearby Walt Disney World. On September 17, 2020, all stores reopened after being closed for a time due to the COVID-19 pandemic in Florida.
Unlike the regular Disney Stores found outside of the parks, Disney Character Warehouses are operated by Disney Parks with their cast members.
